works.description: Mists of Pandaria Secrets is the latest strategy guide for World of Warcraft to hit the market and needless to say covers in depth strategies and walk-throughs for the new MoP expansion. The guides creator Hubert Richardson has put together a series of comprehensive video walk-throughs accompanied by pdf guides, excel spreadsheets, lists, maps, charts and diagrams covering just about every aspect of the new expansion in fine detail.
